  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的流量入口架构图。核心组件有三个：首先是Ingress Controller负责接收外部流量，然后它要依赖Etcd集群做服务发现，最后流量通过LoadBalancer分发到后端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这三个组件的依赖关系能再确认一下吗？Ingress Controller是直接连Etcd，还是通过其他方式获取配置？另外LoadBalancer是在Etcd之后，还是和Ingress Controller平行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Ingress Controller启动时需要从Etcd读取路由配置，所以有一条线指向Etcd。然后Etcd集群本身为了高可用，前面要挂一个LoadBalancer做四层转发。所以顺序是Ingress Controller → Etcd → LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解是链式结构：Ingress Controller作为起点，单向指向Etcd，Etcd再指向LoadBalancer。方向从左到右，用实线连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这样。Etcd到LoadBalancer那条线要注意，这里LoadBalancer是给Etcd集群用的，不是对外的流量入口，别和Ingress Controller的角色搞混了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已绘制完成。三个节点横向排列，Ingress Controller在最左侧，Etcd居中，LoadBalancer在最右侧，两条单向箭头依次连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说反了。重新看一下：Ingress Controller应该直接连LoadBalancer获取入口IP，Etcd是配置中心，Ingress Controller去读Etcd，但LoadBalancer是在Ingress Controller前面还是后面？让我再理清楚——实际上应该是Ingress Controller先经过LoadBalancer做入口，然后去查Etcd？不对，再想想...",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我重新梳理：Ingress Controller作为控制面组件，启动时从Etcd拉取配置（所以连Etcd），而Etcd集群内部为了选主和客户端访问，前面需要LoadBalancer。所以图是对的：Ingress Controller → Etcd → LoadBalancer，不需要修改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认保留当前结构：Ingress Controller指向Etcd，Etcd指向LoadBalancer。这个架构表示控制面组件访问配置中心，配置中心再通过负载均衡保证自身高可用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
